Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.50,00:01:45.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(綱手)嫌な雨が続くな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to this awful rain...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:45.83,00:01:49.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((自来也 : アハハハッ 冗談だ 冗談！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Joking! I'm just joking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:49.34,00:01:52.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(お前には感謝してる))
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, I'm grateful to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.77,00:01:58.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(シズネ)自来也様なら大丈夫です。\Nあの方がそうそう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Jiraiya-sama is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He, of all people, wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.28,00:02:00.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アイツは帰って来ない。\Nえっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:00.95,00:02:04.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私はそっちに賭けた。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I bet him.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.62,00:02:09.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私の賭けは 必ずハズれるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never win my bets.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.46,00:02:12.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そういうことですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.47,00:02:28.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((自来也 : 男はフラれて強くなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rejection makes a man stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.81,00:02:34.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(それに 幸せなんてのは\N男が求めるもんじゃないのぉ))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And besides...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}men aren't the ones\N{\i1}who seek happiness.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:02:34.15,00:02:38.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ かっこつけやがって。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What a poser...
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.49,00:02:45.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,帰って来たら そろそろ\Nかっこつかなくさせてやるかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him keep his cool.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:51.06,00:02:55.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ペイン お前はいったい何者なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain... What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.77,00:03:02.07,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)ペイン それはオレたち\N６人全員を指し示す呼び名だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That name is an alias that\Ndenotes all six of us.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.45,00:03:09.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お お前は その顔…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That face...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:09.78,00:03:13.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弥彦なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that you, Yahiko?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:13.12,00:03:19.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((ああ いたな そんなヤツも。\Nとっくに死んだよ そんなヤツは))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah... There was such a guy,\N{\i1}wasn't there?{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He died a long time ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:19.29,00:03:22.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いったい どういうことだ？\N弥彦は死んだんじゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NI thought you said Yahiko died!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:22.80,00:03:24.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それにその目…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.73,00:03:27.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オレに弥彦の面影を見たか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Yahiko's image in me?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.47,00:03:30.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やはりかつての師ではある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are his former Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:30.50,00:03:33.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが すでに弥彦は死んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yahiko has been dead\Nfor quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.97,00:03:36.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここにいるのは ペインだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains... is Pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:36.48,00:03:41.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんな屁理屈はいい！\Nなぜお前が輪廻眼を持っている！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it with the wordplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you possess the Rinnegan?!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:41.15,00:03:43.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(フカサク)\Nどういうことじゃ 自来也ちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about,\NJiraiya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:43.18,00:03:46.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,かつての\N弟子の１人があのなかにいます。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my former students\Nis among them.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:46.82,00:03:49.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ただその子は\Nあの目を持ってはいなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Except he didn't use to\Npossess those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:49.86,00:03:52.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(シマ)いったい 何が\Nどうなっとるんじゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation is going on?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:52.43,00:03:55.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのなかに\N予言の子が２人もおるんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You saying there are\Ntwo children of prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:55.46,00:03:59.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《いや 違う。 輪廻眼を見て➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's not it either...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I saw the Rinnegan, I convinced\N{\i1}myself that the first one was Nagato...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.20,00:04:02.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最初のヤツを\N長門だと思い込んでしまったが➡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.44,00:04:06.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしが知る長門とは違和感がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he's subtly different\N{\i1}from the Nagato I knew of...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:06.31,00:04:09.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それによく見れば\Nあの６人のなかに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it,\N{\i1}upon closer inspection,{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}none of those six remind me of Nagato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:09.78,00:04:13.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,長門の面影を感じるヤツは\N１人としていない。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:13.28,00:04:15.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それなのに 弥彦の面影を持ち➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other hand,\N{\i1}one of them resembles Yahiko...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:15.95,00:04:18.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,長門の輪廻眼を持つものがいる》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but possesses Nagato's Rinnegan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:18.99,00:04:23.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弥彦なのか 長門なのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you Yahiko... or Nagato?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.46,00:04:26.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前らは いったい何なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly are you?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.36,00:04:29.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,我々は ペイン。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are Pain...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:29.13,00:04:32.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,神だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We are god.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.00,00:04:37.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也ちゃん 退け！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat, Jiraiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.14,00:04:44.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《神だと？》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A god?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:04:48.82,00:04:53.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弥彦 なぜお前が\N長門の目を持っている？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko! How could you possess\NNagato's eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:53.42,00:04:57.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなことを知っても\N我々には勝てん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you knew that,\Nyou could not win!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:05.93,00:05:07.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,小僧！ あきらめんさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lad! Give up already!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:07.87,00:05:10.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんとか 隙を見つけて\N刺し違えてでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find an opening to defeat them,\Neven if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:28.96,00:05:31.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,気配が消えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense his presence...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:37.66,00:05:41.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここは… 結界か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a barrier?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.14,00:05:50.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《胃液？》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gastric fluid?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.01,00:05:54.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,螺旋丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.09,00:06:09.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やったのぉ 自来也ちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Jiraiya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.71,00:06:21.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(シマ)死んだか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.11,00:06:25.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(自来也)結界に引きずり込んで\Nやっとで 一人か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely managed to kill one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,only after dragging it into my barrier...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.45,00:06:33.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か!? 小僧！\Nくっ… なんとか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,00:06:37.46,00:06:40.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,体が… チャクラが乱される！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My body...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My chakra's agitated!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.36,00:06:42.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this?!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.80,00:06:51.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,正体も奇妙じゃけどの 武器まで\N奇妙なものを使うてくるわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identity is a mystery,\Nand they seem to use odd weapons too.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.77,00:06:55.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,コイツらはもう\Nただの人じゃあらへんの。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no longer mortals...\NThey're something entirely different.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.08,00:06:57.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か 別のものじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:59.95,00:07:02.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((誰も 彼の顔を\Nよく知らないし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No one really knows what\Nhe looks like.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:02.42,00:07:04.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,実際には\N存在しないんじゃないか と➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And some claim that\Nhe doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:04.92,00:07:06.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ウワサする者さえいる))
Dialogue: 0,00:07:06.85,00:07:11.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《自来也 : あの顔…\Nヤツは 間違いなく 弥彦だ》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That face...\N{\i1}He is unmistakably Yahiko...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:15.56,00:07:19.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《それなのに\N長門の輪廻眼を持っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet,\N{\i1}he possesses Nagato's Rinnegan...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.93,00:07:23.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弥彦が なんらかの理由で\N長門から奪い取ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Yahiko steal them\N{\i1}from Nagato for some reason?{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:23.77,00:07:28.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし… 他にも\Nあれだけの輪廻眼がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are other\N{\i1}Rinnegan bearers as well...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.64,00:07:30.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いったい どういうことだ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So what's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:33.11,00:07:35.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《それに…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.05,00:07:38.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((自来也 : だが そういう痛みを\N知っているからこそ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding such pain enables you\Nto be kind to others...
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.62,00:07:42.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,人に優しくできることもある。\Nそれが 人だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:42.79,00:07:46.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(長門)それって… どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:46.29,00:07:50.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,成長するってことだのぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called growing up.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:50.13,00:07:54.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(長門)成長するって…\Nつまり どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing up? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:54.10,00:08:00.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(自来也)どうするか\N自分で考えることだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That, you need to figure out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:00.41,00:08:03.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((ここでは人が死にすぎる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many people die here.\NThat pain made me grow up.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:03.24,00:08:06.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(それらの痛みが オレを成長させた))
Dialogue: 0,00:08:06.58,00:08:12.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だとすると\Nやはりコイツが長門か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case,\Ndoes that mean he is Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:12.92,00:08:14.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,んっ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:25.43,00:08:28.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうだ 思い出した！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:28.27,00:08:30.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,コイツは 長門なんかじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is definitely not Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:30.77,00:08:34.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうした!?\Nこの目の前の男➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This fellow before us...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:34.44,00:08:37.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,前に一度\N手合わせしたことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fought him before.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:37.94,00:08:43.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大ガマ仙人の予言に従って\N旅を始めたばかりの頃 出会った➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Fuma Clan member\NI encountered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,right after setting out on my journey,\Nfollowing the Great Lord Elder's prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:43.45,00:08:45.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,風魔一族の男だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.95,00:08:49.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この額の傷は わしがつけたもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him that scar on his forehead...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:49.29,00:08:52.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんで そんなヤツが\Nここにおるんなら？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's a fellow like him\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:52.19,00:08:55.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ますます ペインのことが\Nわからんようになったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm even more confused\Nabout this whole Pain mystery.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:58.00,00:09:01.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((大ガマ仙人 : おぬしは\Nその変革者を導く者じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will guide that revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:01.80,00:09:07.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いずれ おぬしには大きな選択を\N迫られるときが来るじゃろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The day will come when you will be\Nforced to make a critical selection.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.04,00:09:10.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは\Nどうすればいいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What must I do...?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.01,00:09:12.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,正しく選択するには！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make the right choice?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:12.01,00:09:16.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(夢では 世界を歩いて\N本を書いておったのう))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dream, you traveled the world,\Nwriting books.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:16.85,00:09:20.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《まさか 予言のとおりなら…》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be...\N{\i1}If this is the prophecy...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:09:20.69,00:09:26.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは もう一度 ヤツらの前に出て\N確かめたいことがあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to go back and face them\Nin order to confirm something...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:26.53,00:09:28.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お二人は お帰りください。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You two please go back.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:28.66,00:09:30.60,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なに!?\Nダメじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not! You will be killed\Nif you go out again!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:30.60,00:09:34.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,次 出ていけば必ず殺される。\Nさらに眼が増えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They have more eyes,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:34.53,00:09:38.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに結界トラップが二度も通じる\N相手じゃありゃせんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will not fall\Nfor the barrier trap twice!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:38.84,00:09:42.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今 ヤツらは\Nこっちに気づいとらんのじゃけん。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not on to us in here yet.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:42.18,00:09:44.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,逃げるなら今しかない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance to\Nmake a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.11,00:09:47.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今 出て行けば\N殺されるかもしれませんがの。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be killed if I go out there...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:47.98,00:09:52.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 敵の正体を\Nつかめるかもしれません。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I may be able to learn\Nthe truth about them.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:52.62,00:09:54.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この機を逃したら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let this chance slip by,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:54.55,00:09:58.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう ここまでペインに近づける者は\Nたぶん おらんでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anyone else\Nwho could get as close to Pain.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.79,00:10:01.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,正体を見抜くチャンスは 今しかない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance to\Nuncover the truth...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:01.63,00:10:06.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そして… 今こそが\N大ガマ仙人の予言された➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time for selection\Nthat the Great Lord Elder prophesied!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:06.97,00:10:09.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,選択のとき！
Dialogue: 0,00:10:09.30,00:10:12.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,頭と姐さんは\N今までのペインの情報と➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss and Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,please take the intel on Pain\Nwe've gathered so far,
Dialogue: 0,00:10:12.97,00:10:15.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,このペインの死体を\N持って帰ってくだされ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as this corpse and go back.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:15.81,00:10:17.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そして 綱手に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And please tell Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:17.74,00:10:20.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それは\Nかあちゃんだけで十分じゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma should be enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:20.65,00:10:22.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,えっ!? しかし！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:22.58,00:10:24.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,晩飯までに戻りんさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just return by dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:24.82,00:10:27.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ 終わったら\N自来也ちゃんと一緒に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup... When we're done here,\NI'll bring Jiraiya-chan on over with me.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.49,00:10:29.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,飯を食いに帰る。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:35.23,00:10:37.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ありがとう… ございます》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.53,00:11:13.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《やっぱり そうだ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just as I thought!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:17.87,00:11:21.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《コイツら全員\Nわしの会ったことのある忍だ》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all ninjas that\N{\i1}I've encountered before!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:32.82,00:11:38.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《そうか わかったぞ ペインの正体》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've figured out who Pain is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.16,00:11:44.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ノドが…！》\N自来也ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My throat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:11:44.50,00:11:47.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,遅かったな気づくのが。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too late in figuring it out...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:58.51,00:12:03.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ペインの正体\N頭に伝えなくては…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must let Boss know... about\N{\i1}Pain's true identity.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:03.38,00:12:05.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しっかりしろ 自来也ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Jiraiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:07.85,00:12:13.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ダメだ… ノドを潰されたか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good...\N{\i1}My throat has been crushed.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:13.53,00:12:18.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クソッ！ これでは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it... At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:18.40,00:12:22.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ダメだ… 気が遠くなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless... I'm passing out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.80,00:12:28.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは… 死ぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I... going to die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.14,00:12:32.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,失敗なのか？》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I failed...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.16,00:12:49.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《自来也 : 忍は生きざまではなく\N死にざまの世界…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not how you live,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but how you die in\N{\i1}the ninja world...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.83,00:12:54.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍の人生とはどうやって\N生きてきたかではなく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ninja's life is not measured\N{\i1}by how they lived{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.17,00:12:58.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死ぬまでに何をしたかで\Nその価値が決まる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but rather what they managed\N{\i1}to accomplish before their death.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:12:58.84,00:13:04.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,思い返せば\Nわしの人生は失敗ばかりだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking back, my life has\N{\i1}been nothing but failures...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:04.51,00:13:10.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,綱手にフラれ続け\N友を止めることもできず➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continually rejected by Tsunade...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to stop my friend...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.85,00:13:15.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弟子と師を\N守ることもできなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And unable to protect either\N{\i1}my student or my mentor...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:15.72,00:13:21.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影たちが成した偉業に\N比べれば わしのしてきたことは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to the great deeds\N{\i1}of the Hokage,{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my actions are trifling,\N{\i1}insignificant things indeed.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.46,00:13:24.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,取るに足らぬ\Nくだらぬことばかり…。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:24.96,00:13:30.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしも 歴代火影たちのように\N死にたかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish I could have died like\N{\i1}each of the Hokage.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:30.47,00:13:36.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,物語は最後の結びのできで決まる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A tale is only good as\N{\i1}its final turn of events, the plot twist.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.14,00:13:43.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,失敗も一興！ その試練が 己を\N磨いてくれたと信じ 生きてきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Failures must be seen\N{\i1}as mere amusements!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are trials, which hone your skills.\N{\i1}I lived believing that...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:43.48,00:13:48.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その代わり 今までの失敗を\Nチャラにするような➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And in return, I swore I would\N{\i1}accomplish a deed so great{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:48.35,00:13:53.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大きな偉業をなし遂げ\N立派な忍として死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that it would obliterate all\N{\i1}of my failures...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'd die a splendid ninja!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:53.49,00:13:56.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そのはずだった。 フフフ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least, that's how it\N{\i1}was supposed to go...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.40,00:14:02.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが その結び…\N死にざまがこれか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... with my plot twist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My tale, ending like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:02.00,00:14:08.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大ガマ仙人は わしを\N変革者を導く者と予言した。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Great Lord Elder prophesied that\N{\i1}I would guide that revolutionary.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:08.77,00:14:16.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍の世界の安定と破壊に関わる\N大きな選択をする者 と。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person who will make\N{\i1}a great choice{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that will bring either stability\N{\i1}or destruction to the ninja world.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:16.18,00:14:22.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここで ペインを倒し 暁を止め\N忍の世界を救う…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I would defeat Pain,\N{\i1}stop the Akatsuki,{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and save the ninja world\N{\i1}from destruction...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:22.79,00:14:26.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,結局 その選択も\N失敗してしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the end, I failed in\N{\i1}that selection too.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:26.66,00:14:28.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,情けないのぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How pitiful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:28.66,00:14:33.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これが 自来也豪傑物語の\N結びだとはのぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that this will be the twist to\N{\i1}"The Tale of Jiraiya the Gallant".{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:33.80,00:14:37.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くだらぬ物語だった》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a worthless story...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:14:37.14,00:14:39.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((ミナト : いいや\Nそんなことはないです。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.\NThis tale is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:39.81,00:14:42.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この物語は すばらしいです。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:42.48,00:14:46.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,エピソードが 先生の数々の伝説に\Nなぞらえてあって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Each chapter reads like one of\Nyour numerous legendary exploits.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:46.98,00:14:49.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か 自伝小説っぽくて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like an autobiography.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:49.48,00:14:52.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この本の主人公… 最後まで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The main character of this book...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:52.39,00:14:55.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あきらめなかったところが\Nかっこよかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought his determination to\Nnever give up was really cool...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.35,00:14:57.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先生らしいですね この主人公。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lot like you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:57.99,00:15:00.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そ… そうかのぉ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so...?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:00.49,00:15:03.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,で… オレ 思ったんです。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:03.00,00:15:05.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今度 生まれてくる子供も➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope my unborn child
Dialogue: 0,00:15:05.50,00:15:09.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんな主人公みたいな忍に\Nなってくれたらいいな って。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can become a ninja just\Nlike this main character!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:09.37,00:15:14.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから この小説の主人公の名前\Nいただいてもいいですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I'd like your permission\Nto name my son after him.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:14.51,00:15:17.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お… おい！\Nそんなんで いいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:17.41,00:15:20.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ラーメン 食いながら\N適当に決めた名前だぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a random name that\NI thought up while eating ramen.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:20.78,00:15:23.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(クシナ)ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:23.68,00:15:26.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ステキな名前です。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful name.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:28.65,00:15:30.95,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,クシナ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kushina...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:33.36,00:15:37.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アハハハ… ったく… ってことは\Nわしが名づけ親かのぉ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes...\NSo that makes me his godfather?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.33,00:15:40.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わしなんかで 本当にいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.47,00:15:42.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先生だからこそです。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:42.40,00:15:45.97,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,本当の忍の才能を持つ\N立派な忍者で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are a great shinobi who possesses\Nthe true talent of a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.97,00:15:49.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(あなたほどの忍は\Nいませんからね))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other like you.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:49.48,00:15:57.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《そうだ… そうだった。\Nわしは あの子に…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gave that child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:57.35,00:16:00.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((ナルト : オレってば 火影になる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:00.49,00:16:05.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんでもって どの火影をも超える\N火影になるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hokage that surpasses\Nall previous Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.36,00:16:12.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(まっすぐ 自分の言葉は曲げねえ。\Nそれが オレの忍道だ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I never go back on my word...\NThat's my ninja way!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:14.33,00:16:22.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト… 思えば お前は\Nあの小説の主人公どおりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it, Naruto,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you are just like that\N{\i1}novel's main character.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.44,00:16:27.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ミナトとクシナの想い… 願いを\Nちゃんと受け取っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've inherited Minato and\N{\i1}Kushina's wishes, their hopes...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:27.78,00:16:32.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それなのに わしは…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet... I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:32.12,00:16:34.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((先生だからこそです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my sensei!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.45,00:16:37.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,本当の忍の才能を持つ\N立派な忍者で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are a great shinobi who\Npossesses the true talent of a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:37.36,00:16:41.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(あなたほどの忍は\Nいませんからね))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other like you.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.33,00:16:46.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((忍者とは\N忍び堪える者のことなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A ninja is one who endures,\None who stands brave.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:46.47,00:16:49.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ひとつ テメエに教えといてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me teach you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:49.80,00:16:55.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,忍の才能で いちばん大切なのは\N持っている術の数なんかじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important attribute\Nof a ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the number of jutsu he masters.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:55.68,00:17:01.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(大切なのは\Nあきらめねえ ド根性だ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the guts to never give up!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.41,00:17:06.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《まっすぐ\N自分の言葉は曲げない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never go back on your word\N{\i1}and never give up...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:06.35,00:17:09.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そして どんなときも\Nあきらめない。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:09.49,00:17:15.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それが お前の忍道なら…\Nナルトよ！ わしは そのお前の師だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto, if that is your ninja way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then as your mentor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:15.36,00:17:18.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,弱音を吐くわけにはいかんのぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no business whining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.50,00:17:25.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜなら 弟子の忍道は\N師匠ゆずりと相場は決まっとる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For everyone knows that a student\N{\i1}inherits his ninja way from his teacher!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:25.00,00:17:29.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぁ そうだろ？ ナルトよ。 のぉ!!》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that so, Naruto?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:29.84,00:17:33.35,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《気力で吹き返したんか!?》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He fought his way back by sheer will?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:33.35,00:17:36.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,自来也ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:39.52,00:17:42.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心の臓は止まっていたはずだが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure his heart had stopped.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:44.39,00:17:46.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.53,00:17:54.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:54.47,00:17:56.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《あきらめねえ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never give up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.40,00:18:01.87,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それこそが わしの取るべき\N本当の選択だった！》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the true choice\N{\i1}I was supposed to make!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:01.87,00:18:07.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さすがに しぶといな。\N片づける。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite obstinate, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:07.05,00:18:11.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よし！ 確かに受け取ったけんの!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Message received!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:11.55,00:18:15.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ダイイングメッセージ… 暗号化したか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A dying message...\NHe wrote it in code, eh?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:18.42,00:18:23.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト… 予言の子は\N間違いなくお前だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto... You are the child of prophecy,\N{\i1}I'm sure of it now.{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:23.50,00:18:27.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あとは… すべて託すぞ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I entrust you with the rest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.05,00:18:44.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カエルには逃げられたか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The frog... got away.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:49.19,00:18:53.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《自来也豪傑物語…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Tale of Jiraiya the Gallant"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:53.03,00:18:56.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これで ちったぁ\Nマシになったかのぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now it'll end a bit better I hope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:56.86,00:19:05.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最終章… 井の中の蛙\N大海で散る… の巻か。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final chapter will be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Frog in the Well Drifts\N{\i1}Into the Great Ocean."{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:05.54,00:19:11.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ほどほどに\Nあっぱれ あっぱれ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not bad... Not bad at all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.88,00:19:17.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さて… そろそろ\Nペンを置くとしよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now... It's about time\N{\i1}I put down my pen...{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:17.55,00:19:23.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,おお… そうだ！\N続編のタイトルは 何がいいかのぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, that's right!\N{\i1}What should I name the sequel?{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:23.36,00:19:28.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうだのぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:28.49,00:19:35.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,『うずまきナルト物語』\Nうむ… それが いい…》
